    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to level 1 (not-assessed) per MRL 2 requirements. Grid convergence, output comparison, and validation relevance evidence collectively support the claim that the CFD model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. Re-validation of the geometry and boundary condition dataset against the January 2026 model revision is planned prior to the next regulatory submission cycle.",
